Step 1 — Login:
User app open karta hai, Auth Service pe login karta hai, accessToken milta hai jo har request me use hoga.
Step 2 — Location save:
User map pe pickup aur dropoff pin lagata hai. Frontend Google Maps se coordinates leke Location Service ko bhejta hai. Do locationId milte hain.
Step 3 — Ride create/join:
Pehla user ride create karta hai, rideId milta hai. Baaki 2-3 users same rideId se join karte hain. Ab ek "room" ban gayi.
Step 4 — Real-time tracking:
Sab users Socket.io se connect hote hain us rideId ke room me. Cab har 3-5 second me location bhejti hai. Sab room members ko cab_location_updated event milta hai. Frontend map pe car animate karta hai.
JWT token ka role:
Ek hi token Auth Service banta hai — Location Service bhi same secret se verify karta hai. Koi alag connection nahi dono services ke beech. 🎯





